00:34:24,080 --> 00:34:24,670
Come down.

1142
00:34:24,670 --> 00:34:25,150
Help him.

1143
00:34:28,100 --> 00:34:31,460
(Ning, Jin, He, Ding, Ke. Total.)

1144
00:34:31,710 --> 00:34:32,280
Okay?

1145
00:34:32,280 --> 00:34:32,840
Any shock left?

1146
00:34:35,190 --> 00:34:38,560
