1148
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:41,360
Right?

1149
00:34:45,150 --> 00:34:46,320
(Beginner Trial Stage Two Cleared)
Stage Two

1150
00:34:46,320 --> 00:34:46,880
cleared.

1151
00:34:47,840 --> 00:34:49,080
Stage Three has started.

1152
00:34:49,710 --> 00:34:51,080
The purpose of this trial

1153
00:34:51,080 --> 00:34:52,630
is to test your endurance

1154
00:34:52,630 --> 00:34:53,800
and reasoning skills.

1155
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:56,560
(Stage Three may be electrified)
Among these 50 buttons,

1156
00:34:56,560 --> 00:34:59,120
(Endurance and Reasoning Skills)
15 are unpowered,

1157
00:34:59,120 --> 00:35:01,940
