You're in the best shape.

1215
00:36:41,240 --> 00:36:41,680
You know?

1216
00:36:42,880 --> 00:36:43,400
Exactly.

1217
00:36:43,880 --> 00:36:44,560
Alright, let's do this.

1218
00:36:44,560 --> 00:36:45,240
One and ten.

1219
00:36:46,920 --> 00:36:48,560
