It's live.

1222
00:36:55,800 --> 00:36:56,560
Two and nine.

1223
00:37:00,460 --> 00:37:01,460
(2 and 9 failed)

1224
00:37:01,640 --> 00:37:02,120
Three and eight.

1225
00:37:05,340 --> 00:37:06,260
(3 and 8 failed)

1226
00:37:06,520 --> 00:37:07,520
Four and seven.

1227
00:37:10,100 --> 00:37:11,100
(4 and 7 failed)

1228
00:37:11,120 --> 00:37:12,280
There's more.

1229
00:37:12,340 --> 00:37:14,140
