1234
00:37:22,200 --> 00:37:22,920
It's okay.

1235
00:37:22,920 --> 00:37:23,800
I can take it.

1236
00:37:23,800 --> 00:37:24,200
Really,

1237
00:37:24,200 --> 00:37:25,040
I'm fine.

1238
00:37:25,040 --> 00:37:25,880
Still hanging in there.

1239
00:37:25,880 --> 00:37:26,700
(Big brother mode activated)

1240
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:29,120
