1241
00:37:29,140 --> 00:37:32,940
(There's no way
we're that unlucky, right?)

1242
00:37:33,020 --> 00:37:35,780
(They were that unlucky)

1243
00:37:35,800 --> 00:37:36,480
Still live.

1244
00:37:38,240 --> 00:37:39,040
Again.

1245
00:37:39,040 --> 00:37:40,240
No way there isn't
a single unpowered pair.

1246
00:37:40,920 --> 00:37:41,320
There is.

1247
00:37:41,760 --> 00:37:42,200
There is.

1248
00:37:42,640 --> 00:37:43,400
There is. I...

1249
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:43,900
(Completely out of ideas)

1250
00:37:44,180 --> 00:37:45,600
(All 25 attempts failed)

1251
00:37:45,600 --> 00:37:46,160
Let me try.

1252
00:37:46,220 --> 00:37:48,220
(Cheerful)

1253
00:37:48,240 --> 00:37:49,360
Let's eliminate the last row.

1254
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:50,960
Match the second-to-last row
with the first row moving inward.

1255
00:37:50,960 --> 00:37:52,400
(Starting Plan B)
Okay, let's do one and nine.

1256
00:37:52,400 --> 00:37:52,680
Right.

1257
00:37:53,440 --> 00:37:53,880
One and nine.

1258
00:37:53,940 --> 00:37:55,100
(Will the smiling boy)

1259
00:37:55,100 --> 00:37:56,900
(finally get lucky?)

1260
00:37:57,460 --> 00:37:58,980
(1 and 9 failed)

1261
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:00,000
Two and eight.

1262
00:38:00,620 --> 00:38:02,100
(2 and 8 failed)

1263
00:38:02,120 --> 00:38:02,880
Three and seven.

1264
00:38:04,260 --> 00:38:06,300
(3 and 7 succeeded)

1265
00:38:09,060 --> 00:38:10,820
(First successful match)

1266
00:38:13,920 --> 00:38:14,600
