1284
00:38:43,360 --> 00:38:44,000
Nice.

1285
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:44,560
Three and fourteen.

1286
00:38:45,340 --> 00:38:46,160
(3 and 14 failed)

1287
00:38:46,160 --> 00:38:46,920
Three and fifteen.

1288
00:38:47,160 --> 00:38:47,560
Three and fifteen.

1289
