1304
00:39:09,120 --> 00:39:11,480
Three, seven, eleven, thirteen...

1305
00:39:11,480 --> 00:39:12,320
Fifteen wasn't one.

1306
00:39:12,320 --> 00:39:12,880
Seventeen was.

1307
