That's it.

1315
00:39:28,320 --> 00:39:28,800
Nice.

1316
00:39:28,800 --> 00:39:29,400
How many do we have now?

1317
00:39:29,400 --> 00:39:30,400
Then we just list

1318
00:39:30,400 --> 00:39:31,560
