1319
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:32,840
Done.

1320
00:39:32,840 --> 00:39:33,400
Okay.

1321
00:39:33,720 --> 00:39:37,360
Three, seven, eleven, thirteen,

1322
00:39:37,360 --> 00:39:39,240
seventeen, nineteen,

1323
00:39:39,240 --> 00:39:40,520
twenty-three,

1324
00:39:40,520 --> 00:39:41,560
twenty-nine,

1325
00:39:41,560 --> 00:39:42,880
thirty-one,

1326
00:39:42,880 --> 00:39:44,240
thirty-seven,

1327
00:39:44,240 --> 00:39:45,360
forty-one,

1328
00:39:45,360 --> 00:39:45,920
forty-three,

1329
00:39:45,920 --> 00:39:46,480
