1397
00:41:55,320 --> 00:41:56,560
Familiar rules.

1398
00:41:57,000 --> 00:41:58,040
But they mentioned one key detail.

1399
00:41:58,040 --> 00:41:59,240
They said, "Among the suspects,

1400
00:41:59,240 --> 00:42:00,800
