"I don't want to use my card".

1546
00:45:28,840 --> 00:45:29,840
That instantly makes them suspicious.

1547
00:45:30,920 --> 00:45:31,720
Exactly.

1548
00:45:32,960 --> 00:45:35,200
If we reach a critical clue
during the review...

1549
00:45:35,200 --> 00:45:35,560
No need.

1550
00:45:35,560 --> 00:45:37,040
I already figured it out earlier.

1551
00:45:37,040 --> 00:45:37,760
(Suspicion level instantly maxed out)

1552
00:45:37,760 --> 00:45:39,360
No need. Using it would just waste it.

1553
00:45:40,480 --> 00:45:41,080
Alright.

