It's this room.

1605
00:47:23,000 --> 00:47:23,320
(Unlocking "Uncertain Events")

1606
00:47:23,320 --> 00:47:24,120
Wait.

1607
00:47:24,120 --> 00:47:25,100
(Explore scenes. Unlock new areas)

1608
00:47:27,000 --> 00:47:28,600
(Search for clues.)
Search corners no one pays attention to.

1609
00:47:29,080 --> 00:47:30,000
(Collect clues and reconstruct the case)
There's a corpse!

1610
00:47:32,200 --> 00:47:33,760
Use the Lights On Card.

1611
00:47:33,920 --> 00:47:35,040
(Skill Card)
Use a skill card.

1612
00:47:35,040 --> 00:47:36,040
(Source, one free card for first login.)
Don't force yourself.

1613
00:47:36,040 --> 00:47:36,960
It's okay.

1614
00:47:36,960 --> 00:47:38,160
(Time Extension Card, extra stage time.)
I have a Time Extension Card.

1615
00:47:38,160 --> 00:47:39,880
(Lights Out Card, lights off once.)
Lights out, close your eyes.

1616
00:47:39,880 --> 00:47:40,640
(Soothing Card, Calm NPC emotions.)
Soothing Card.

1617
00:47:40,640 --> 00:47:41,100
(With 10+ clues, some incorrect)

1618
00:47:41,100 --> 00:47:41,520
(options are cut.)
Elimination Card.

1619
00:47:41,520 --> 00:47:42,360
Ding, use Restore Card.

1620
00:47:42,360 --> 00:47:43,720
Then restore this mirror.

1621
00:47:43,720 --> 00:47:44,840
Can it restore that?

1622
00:47:44,840 --> 00:47:45,320
(Restore Card, restore one clue)
Okay.

1623
00:47:45,320 --> 00:47:46,840
I can't believe that actually worked.

1624
00:47:46,840 --> 00:47:47,800
Seriously?

1625
00:47:47,800 --> 00:47:48,200
Wait,

1626
00:47:48,600 --> 00:47:49,040
guys.

1627
00:47:50,000 --> 00:47:51,240
(Stamina Points)
Collect stamina points.

1628
00:47:51,240 --> 00:47:52,120
(Stamina drops randomly in dungeons.)
Without stamina,

1629
00:47:52,120 --> 00:47:53,240
(Use stamina to get food supplies.)
you literally can't eat.

1630
00:47:53,240 --> 00:47:54,000
I want food.

1631
00:47:54,480 --> 00:47:55,160
I'm elder than you.

1632
00:47:55,160 --> 00:47:56,040
Give it to the youngest.

1633
00:47:56,440 --> 00:47:57,680
Still thinking about food right now?

1634
00:47:57,680 --> 00:47:59,640
You're still thinking about eating now?

1635
00:47:59,640 --> 00:48:01,240
I didn't even bring my meal card.

1636
00:48:01,400 --> 00:48:02,680
You guys are unbelievable.

1637
00:48:02,680 --> 00:48:03,400
Beg me.

1638
00:48:03,640 --> 00:48:05,800
Please, Ding.

1639
00:48:07,040 --> 00:48:08,000
What the hell?

1640
00:48:08,000 --> 00:48:08,920
Take it.

1641
00:48:08,920 --> 00:48:10,600
Next episode, I'm taking that.

1642
00:48:11,160 --> 00:48:12,080
(Side Quest)
Help them out.

1643
00:48:12,080 --> 00:48:12,920
(Triggered by players or NPCs.)
Earn their trust.

1644
00:48:12,920 --> 00:48:14,240
(Side quests raise trust or rewards.)
Only then can we proceed.

1645
00:48:14,240 --> 00:48:15,440
(Players may accept or refuse.)
There are too many files.

1646
00:48:15,440 --> 00:48:16,600
(Accept File Sorting Quest? Yes / No)
Think of a solution, please.

1647
00:48:16,600 --> 00:48:18,520
(Accept Groom Rehearsal Quest? Yes / No)
Just a rehearsal groom stand-in.

1648
00:48:18,520 --> 00:48:19,000
(Accept Puppet Guard Quest? Yes / No)

1649
00:48:19,000 --> 00:48:19,600
Must protect it.

1650
00:48:20,120 --> 00:48:20,620
(Accept Hit Single Act Quest? Yes / No)

1651
00:48:20,620 --> 00:48:21,080
I'm Li Fei.

1652
00:48:21,080 --> 00:48:21,920
I have no spine.

1653
00:48:21,920 --> 00:48:22,600
Unaffected by gain

1654
00:48:22,600 --> 00:48:23,900
(Side Quest Complete)
or loss.

1655
00:48:26,000 --> 00:48:26,800
(Court Session)
Talk properly with people.

1656
00:48:26,800 --> 00:48:27,440
(Detectives may start court hearings.)

1657
00:48:27,440 --> 00:48:28,120
(Interrogate a suspect for 10 minutes)
No disadvantage.

1658
00:48:28,120 --> 00:48:30,040
(Advance the deduction process.)
What are you all doing?

1659
00:48:30,040 --> 00:48:31,320
We're investigating a case.

1660
00:48:31,320 --> 00:48:32,600
But that has nothing to do with me.

1661
00:48:32,600 --> 00:48:33,840
I don't know what you mean.

1662
00:48:33,840 --> 00:48:35,640
Then the word 'steal' doesn't fit.

1663
00:48:35,800 --> 00:48:36,960
Why did they do all this?

1664
00:48:36,960 --> 00:48:38,320
Wasn't it because of how you hurt

1665
00:48:38,320 --> 00:48:39,320
them when they were young?

1666
00:48:39,440 --> 00:48:40,680
You're linking

1667
00:48:40,680 --> 00:48:41,920
those two things together?

1668
00:48:41,920 --> 00:48:43,920
Of course. Can they really be separated?

1669
00:48:43,920 --> 00:48:45,680
This is trauma caused by my family.

1670
00:48:45,680 --> 00:48:46,600
Then tell us.

1671
00:48:46,600 --> 00:48:48,360
Who exactly is that child's father?

1672
00:48:48,920 --> 00:48:49,240
What?

1673
00:48:50,640 --> 00:48:51,960
Drag him out.

1674
00:48:51,960 --> 00:48:52,720
Guards!

1675
00:48:52,880 --> 00:48:54,880
(Main Quest)
But all of that is just setup.

1676
00:48:54,880 --> 00:48:56,760
(Progress the case to uncover truth.)
